get.description:
Lists the Helm releases in the specified namespace.

Success response:
    { "success": true, "data": [ ...releases... ] }
Empty list if the namespace exists but has no releases:
    { "success": true, "data": [] }
HTTP 403 if the SA does not have permissions on the namespace Secrets.

Returns the fleet status.
If refresh=true, forces an immediate scan (slow);
otherwise returns the cached result (instant).
